The Chief of Staff to Kwara State Government, Adisa Logun, is dead. Logun, it was gathered, died at an Ilorin hospital on Tuesday afternoon. The septuagenarian was reportedly rushed to the hospital on Monday evening as a result of undisclosed health complications and finally passed away on Tuesday. The state government has however not officially announced his death though close family relatives have confirmed. It was not clear as of press time whether the death of the CoS was due to Covid-19 complications or not. Details laterâ€¦ 